<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    
        <header >
            <h1>User Profile: <%= username %></h1>
        </header>


      <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a><br>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
        </nav>

        <section id="profile-content">
           
                <h2>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h2>
                <p>Here you can manage and personalize your profile settings.</p>
                <p>Let’s make this experience all about you!</p>
       
        </section>


        <section id="activity-section">
            <h2>Your Recent Activity</h2>
            <p>Keep track of your recent interactions and contributions here.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Activity 1: Updated profile details.</li>
                <li>Activity 2: Liked a Valentine’s story.</li>
                <li>Activity 3: Shared a memory.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="favorites-section">
            <h2>Your Favorites</h2>
            <p>Discover and manage your favorite features or items:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Saved Valentine’s cards.</li>
                <li>Favorite profiles.</li>
                <li>Most loved features.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="settings-section">
            <h2>Manage Settings</h2>
            <p>Take control of your profile and privacy settings:</p>
            <button>Edit Profile</button>
            <button>Privacy Settings</button>
        </section>

       
      </div>

    <footer >
        <p>&copy; 2025 Chahinez. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>